Write a java program using ArrayList to display the following output:

LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Java]
Updated LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Kotlin]

//Code here
//LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Java]
//Updated LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Kotlin]
import java.util.*;
public class collection
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        LinkedList li=new LinkedList();
        li.add("Java");
        li.add("Python");
        li.add("JavaScript");
        li.add("Java");
        System.out.println("LinkedList: "+li);
        li.set(3,"Kotlin");
        System.out.println("Updated LinkedList: "+li);
    }
}

